text:
[Verse]
Stars in the sky
Shining so high
They make me sigh
A lullaby

[Verse 2]
Moonlight's embrace
Lighting my face
In this vast space
We find our place

[Chorus]
Starlit night
Oh what a sight
Hold me tight
Till morning light

[Verse 3]
Dreams take flight
In pure delight
Hearts so light
In the starlit night

[Verse 4]
Cosmic dance
Lost in trance
This romance
Our sweet chance

[Bridge]
Wish on a star
Dreams not far
Here we are
Hearts ajar
title: Starlit Night
